  <prompt>Edit `BuildNotificationEntity` at `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Nodes/CreateNotificationNodeExecutor.cs` lines 471-546. Extend the customData JSON shape to include: `regardingName`, `regardingEntityType`, `regardingId`, `viaMatter` (object: `id`, `name`, `memberships[]` — one entry per role), and `source` (object: `entityType`, `id`, `modifiedOn`, `owningUser`). When the source-record has no matter linkage, omit the `viaMatter` field entirely. When the source-record has multiple membership roles (owner + assignedAttorney, etc.), `viaMatter.memberships` is an array with one entry per role. Preserve the existing fields (`category`, `priority`, `actionUrl`, `dueDate`) and the idempotency check `CheckForDuplicateNotificationAsync`.</prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform developer. Follow ADRs strictly. BFF NodeExecutor specialist — extends existing CreateNotificationNodeExecutor in a backward-compatible way per ADR-013 and CLAUDE.md §10.</role>

